high_descs: Turn to the right, and go to the brown table.
Pick up the lettuce from the front of the table.
Take the lettuce and turn around to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the lettuce inside, shut the door. Open the door again to take the lettuce out and shut the door.
Take the lettuce and turn around. Go across the room and turn right at the far counter.
Place the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Take lettuce to the fridge, followed by the sink.

high_descs: Move to table across from the fridge to the right of the door.
Pick up lettuce from the tab;e.
Move to the fridge behind you to the left of the door.
Place lettuce inside and chill for a moment before removing and closing the door.
Move to the sink behind you and to the right of the table/
Put the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled lettuce in the sink from the table.

high_descs: Move forward, then turn right to approach the table.
Pick up the lettuce on the table.
Go to the fridge behind you.
Chill the lettuce in the fridge.
Turn left, move forward, turn left, move forward, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink to the left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put cold lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Go forward, then turn to the right and go to the table.
Pick up the lettuce that is on the table.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the lettuce in, close the fridge, then take the lettuce out of the fridge.
Turn to the left, go forward, turn to the left and go to the sink on your right.
Put the lettuce in left side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put cold lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right to go to the wooden table.
Take the lettuce on the table.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator.
Place the lettuce inside the refrigerator to chill it and then take it out.
Take the chilled lettuce to the kitchen sink to the left.
Place the lettuce inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled lettuce in the sink.
